<section class="flex flex-col border border-gray-300 rounded-3xl justify-center height-fit">
  <h2 class="text-center py-4 border-b border-gray-200 font-bold capitalize text-lg">Technical SEO</h2>
  <div class="flex flex-col">
    <div class="border-b border-gray-200 p-4 flex flex-col">
      <span class="font-bold capitalize mb-3">Site Speed:</span>
      <p>Make sure your pages load quickly. Use tools like PageSpeed Insights to diagnose issues.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="border-b border-gray-200 p-4 flex flex-col">
      <span class="font-bold capitalize mb-3">Mobile-friendliness:</span>
      <p>Google favors mobile-first optimization. Check how your site looks on different devices.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="border-gray-200 p-4 flex flex-col">
      <span class="font-bold capitalize mb-3">XML Sitemap:</span>
      <p>Submit a sitemap to tell search engines about all pages on your site.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="border-gray-200 p-4 flex flex-col">
      <span class="font-bold capitalize mb-3">Robots.txt:</span>
      <p>Guide search engines on which pages should and shouldn't be crawled.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>